original: Dahlström, Gustaf Nils Ragnar, taxeringsintendent, Mariestad, f. 14/2/ 95 i Sundsvall _ av bokhåll. Anders Gustaf D. o. Hanna Augusta Kling. G. 38 m. Irma Wapian. Barn: Ulf Ragnar f. 42. — Jur. kand. v. Sthlms högsk. 20. Not. i norra Hähingl. doms. 20, i Finspånga 1. här. doms. 22, tjg. v. länsstyr. i östergötl. 1. i Linköp. 24 o. i Skarab. 1. i Mariestad, tf. länsassess. där 39, taxiint. fr. 44. RVOlkl.
translated: Dahlström, Gustaf Nils Ragnar, tax assessment superintendent, Mariestad, b. February 14, 1895 in Sundsvall, son of accountant Anders Gustaf D. and Hanna Augusta Kling. Married in 1938 to Irma Wapian. Children: Ulf Ragnar, born in 1942. He graduated with a law degree from Stockholm University in 1920. Became a notary in the northern Hälsingland district in 1920, in Finspång for the first district court in 1922, served as an official with the county administration in Östergötland in 1923, in Linköping in 1924, and in Skaraborg in Mariestad in 1931. Served as acting county assessor in Mariestad in 1939, and tax assessment superintendent from 1944. Awarded the Royal Order of the Polar Star.

awards.name: Royal Order of the Polar Star
